00:06:35.549 --> 00:06:38.580
Example, one question.

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:41.820
What is the two digit number statements?

00:06:42.179 --> 00:06:44.414
One, the sum of the digits is nine.

00:06:45.165 --> 00:06:50.505
Two, the digit in the 10 is twice
the digit in the units place options.

00:06:51.180 --> 00:06:54.719
A statement one alone is
sufficient to answer the question.

00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:58.650
B. Statement two alone is
sufficient to answer the question.

00:06:58.980 --> 00:07:03.120
C. Both statement one and statement
two together are sufficient to

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:06.390
